race.description: Jgp We Stand With Tassie Preferential Box Draw Mas
race.comment: TOO MUCH SCOTCH (8) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.03. Draws out wide but goes well over this trip. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 11 starts. Well placed and can measure up. LONE HUNTER (5) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 3 (20.15). Will need some luck early after drawing a tricky box here. Form should stack up. BYE BYE TAIPAN (7) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 366m at this track, taking a Mix 5 in a solid 19.83. Top win two back and can measure up again. ARCHIE TRICK (1) placed last time and is worth some thought.
